text_question_merge: Unganidza mabhukumaki aripo neakatorwa mabhukumaka kana kuatsiva?
text_importexport_content: Pano unogona kuendesa kunze kwenyika mabhukumaka ako muNetscape fomati.
text_help_content1: Mabhukumaki Maneja chikumbiro chinobatsira kuchengetedza uye kugadzirisa internet mabhukumaki.
text_help_content2: Kugadzira bhukumaki nyowani, kana dhairekitori nyowani, pinda iyo "kuwedzera" icon: sarudza pakati pebhukumaki nefaira, isa zita uye pakupedzisira URL, wobva wadzvanya saiti kuti uchengetedze shanduko, kana kudzvanya bvisa kudzima bhukumaki, kana kudzoka kusvetuka shanduko asi chengeta bhukumaki.
text_help_content3: Dhinda bhatani "vhura" padhuze nebhukumaki kuti uzarure inoenderana URL.
text_help_content4: Dhinda bhatani re "wedzera" mukati mefaira kuti uwedzere chinhu chitsva pairi.
text_help_content5: Kune ese mabhukumaki uye maforodha, tinya bhatani re "edit" kuti uvashandure, pinda bhatani re "dzokera kumashure" kuchinjana chinzvimbo nechinhu chakapfuura, pinda bhatani re "enda kumberi" kuchinjana chinzvimbo nechinhu chinotevera, tinya "enda kumusoro" bhatani kuburitsa chinhu kubva mufaira kwazviri parizvino, kana kudzvanya bhatani "enda pasi" kufambisa chinhu mukati meiyo inotevera subfolder.
text_help_content6: Mune iyo menyu yekumisikidza, inokwanisika mushure mekubaya pane iyo "marongero" icon, unogona kuviga kana kuratidza ekugadzirisa, ekufambisa uye ekuwedzera mabhatani. Izvo zvakare zvinoita kuti uchinje mutauro weiye mushandisi interface.
text_help_content7: Kupinza kana kutumira kunze mabhukumaki, tinya pane yekunze / yekunze icon. Iyo HTML Netscape Mabhukumaki fomati inotsigirwa, saka zvinokwanisika kuendesa mabhukumaki anotumirwa neakakura mawebhu mabhurawuza. Kana uchinotora mabhukumaki kubva kufaira, mabhukumaki aripo anozobviswa uye kunyorwa.
text_help_content8: Mabhukumaki Maneja ndeye Progressive Web Chikumbiro, zvinoreva kuti inomhanya mukati mebhurawuza. Kana iwe ukaiisa, nepo mabrowser zvinhu asiri kuratidzwa, ichiri kumhanya mukati mebhurawuza. Mabhukumaki anochengetwa munzvimbo yebrowser yeKuchengeterwa kwemabhukumaki.marcoparrone.com domain. localStorage inoshanda zvakanaka ne Chrome, Edge uye Firefox mabhurawuza. Mamwe mabhurawuza anogona kudzima LocalStorage mushure menguva yakati. Android nekumisikidza inoshandisa Chrome, Windows nokusarudzika inoshandisa Edge. Mabhukumaki Maneja parizvino haitsigirwe pane zvigadzirwa zveApple. Nechinangwa chekubatsira kudzivirira kurasikirwa kwemabhukumaki, zvinokurudzirwa kuita backup uchishandisa iko "kutumira" mashandiro, pese paunoita zvimwe zvaunogadzirisa zvausingade kurasikirwa nazvo.

text_about_content5: Iri dandemutande reApp rakashandurwa kuti zvive nyore uchishandisa software yekushandura inofambiswa neGoogle Dudziro. Kuyedza kunonzwisisika kwakaitwa kupa shanduro chaiyo, zvisinei, hapana shanduro yakazvimiririra haina kukwana kana kuitirwa kutsiva vashanduri vevanhu. Dudziro dzinopihwa sevhisi kune vashandisi vewe marcoparrone.com webhusaiti, uye zvinopihwa "sezvazviri." Hapana garandi yerudzi rupi zvarwo, ingave yakaratidzwa kana kurehwa, inoitwa nezvekururama, kuvimbika, kana kururamisa kweshanduro dzese dzakaitwa kubva kuChirungu kuenda mune chero mumwe mutauro. Zvimwe zvemukati (zvakadai semifananidzo, mavhidhiyo, Flash, nezvimwewo) zvinogona kusanyatso dudzirwa nekuda kwekukanganisa kwesoftware yekushandura.
text_about_content6: Chinyorwa chepamutemo ndicho chinyorwa cheChirungu chewebhu webhusaiti. Chero kusanzwanana kana mutsauko unogadzirwa mushanduro hausunge uye hauna mvumo yepamutemo yekuteerera kana kuita zvinangwa. Kana paine chero mibvunzo inomuka inoenderana nekururama kweruzivo rwuri mune yakadudzirwa webhusaiti, tarisa kune yeChirungu vhezheni yewebhusaiti inova yepamutemo vhezheni.
